Package application.users

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuestI
    Interface that models the functionality required for Guests in the app
    HostI
    Interface that models the functionality required for Hosts in the app
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Class that stores all the data of an Admin.
    Guest
    Class that stores all the data of a Guest.
    Host
    Class that stores all the data of a Host.
    MultiRoleUser
    Class that contains all the data of a Registered User that is simulatneously Host and Guest.
    RegisteredUser
    This class contains everything related to the users and their types.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RegisteredUser.Role
    This enumeration is used to distinguish between all the types of users, without having to check the class of a Java Object
